<H3> <TI>   Rumors of Aircraft Carriers Deployment Denied </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2901024094 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network in Korean 0200 GMT 29 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2901024094 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Korean </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In connection with rumors that U.S. aircraft 
carriers would be deployed in the vicinity of the Korean 
peninsula, an ROK Government official said today that the ROK 
Government has not been informed of such deployment. He also 
said he knew this is not true. This official also said that 
when the Team Spirit exercise is conducted, U.S. forces aircraft 
