  During his stay in Pyongyang, Graham is expected to meet 
President Kim Il-song and officiate service at the Pongsu church 
in Pyongyang. 
  This is Graham's second visit to North Korea. During his 
first visit in April 1992, he conferred with Kim Il-song and 
gave a lecture at Kim Il-song University. 

