  [Text] 
Looking at the products exported to Japan (re-imports), we 
see that they range widely from audio and video equipment such 
as VTR's and televisions to office equipment and high tech 
semiconductors and electronic parts. Thus, along with active 
local production in Asia, there has been a growth in exports to 
the region of semiconductors and electronic parts (primarily 
used for assembling consumer appliances and electronic 
equipment), which are hard to secure locally (Table 15). 


