                  to the      1993         to the      1993         to the 
                  same                     same                     same 
                  period                   period                   period 
                  1992                     1992                     1992 

                  100         Percent      100         Percent      100         Percent 
                  million                  million                  million 
                  yen                      yen                      yen 

