  [Text] Pyongyang, February 1 (KCNA) -- President Kim 
Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea on January 
29 sent a message to Yasir 'Arafat, president of the state of 
Palestine and chairman of the Executive Committee of the 
Palestine Liberation Organisation, in reply to his message of 
solidarity on the New Year 1994. 
  In the reply message, President Kim Il-song said that the 
