form of confederation is a great encouragement to the Korean 
people. 
  Expressing the belief that the friendly relations between 
the 
two peoples would grow stronger and develop, President Kim 
Il-song heartily wished the Palestinian president and people 
greater success in their struggle to restore their legitimate 
national rights and completely solve the Palestinian issue. 

