  [Text] Hanoi VNA Feb. 1 -- National Assembly Chairman Nong 
Duc Manh received here this afternoon Indonesian Ambassador to 
Vietnam Mr. Juana who paid him a farewell visit at the end of 
his term of office in Vietnam. At the reception, Chairman Nong 
Duc Manh highly valued Mr. Juana's contributions to the 
promotion of the friendship and cooperation between Vietnam and 
