<F P=101> Cambodia </F>
<H3> <TI>   VGNUFC Condemns French Over Succession </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK0202035594 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0202035594 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Cambodian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Recently, (Misac), a former French minister, came 
to Phnom Penh and went around asking about the so-called 
successor to His Majesty King Norodom Sihanouk. 
  (Misac)'s activity can be compared to a merchant getting 
ready to buy a tiger's hide. This is France's policy and 
preparation for Cambodia in line with its obsolete colonialist 
system. 
  During this trip to sound out the opinion on this important 
issue, (Misac) received answers from various sources as follows: 
  First opinion: The persons qualified to succeed his majesty 
are members of the Duang Dynasty's Norodom and Sisowat lines, 
such as His Royal Highness [HRH] Prince Krompreah Norodom 
Ranariddh, Norodom Chakkrapong, HRH Prince Kromluong Yuveakneat, 
and Prince Norodom Sihamoni. 
  Second opinion: The Vietnamese communists and their puppets 
want Norodom Chakkrapong to succeed His Majesty Norodom 
Sihanouk. They have also put Chea Sim's name on the list to 
succeed his majesty, saying that Chea Sim has been given a royal 
title. He has ordered the masses and government officials to 
use royal language when addressing him and to call his wife the 
royal consort. 
  The people in Phnom Penh ridiculed traitor Chea Sim, 
likening 
him to the lizard with a golden ring. They asked, who asked 
(Misac) to come to Phnom Penh to arrange an heir to His Majesty 
King Norodom Sihanouk's throne -- the outstanding leader and 
father of the nation, of national reconciliation, and of peace 
-- who is respected and loved by the entire nation? 
  The Cambodian nation and people asked, who wanted this man 
to 
raise the question of reigning on the throne in the current 
Cambodian situation when the nation and people are suffering 
from great and most serious misery due to both national and 
social problems and despite the fact that His Majesty King 
Norodom Sihanouk still continues as the esteemed and beloved 
outstanding leader of the nation and people? 
  The nation and people also expressed anger with the 
Vietnamese communists and their puppets for trying to elevate 
the traitorous clique, their out-and-out flunky to the throne in 
Cambodia. 
  His Majesty Norodom Sihanouk has stated clearly that the 
reigning king must have good quality and virtue and always be 
concerned about the national and people's interests and the 
national unity, sovereignty, and territorial integrity of 
Cambodia. The entire Cambodian nation and people are in unity 
with His Majesty Norodom Sihanouk. Therefore, France, the 
Vietnamese communists, or any other foreigners have no right to 
arrange any successor to the throne for serving them and 
destroying the Cambodian nation and people. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

